<span id="freeTextContainer10985663105408776554">Terror seen through the eyes of a twelve year-old girl, this is a memoir of the Cultural Revolution as much as a truly harrowing horror story where relatives &amp; friends betray each other for no reason. The zombification of the Chinese under Mao&apos;s rule is distinctively awful, a mindset and time that must never be repeated (but under Trump&apos;s potential presidency, possibly might*).<br/><br/>*Oracle time!-- wow do I feel dumb now.</span>
  <span id="freeText10985663105408776554" style="display:none">Terror seen through the eyes of a twelve year-old girl, this is a memoir of the Cultural Revolution as much as a truly harrowing horror story where relatives &amp; friends betray each other for no reason. The zombification of the Chinese under Mao's rule is distinctively awful, a mindset and time that must never be repeated (but under Trump's potential presidency, possibly might*).<br /><br />*Oracle time!-- wow do I feel dumb now.</span>
